-- Ex-Brocade Chief Reyes Sentenced to 18 Months for Stock Option Backdating
-- Karen Gullo
-- 2010-06-24T18:01:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-24/ex-brocade-chief-reyes-sentenced-to-18-months-for-stock-option-backdating.html

          
          
             Greg Reyes, former chief executive
officer at Brocade Communications Systems Inc., was sentenced to
18 months in prison for backdating employee stock-option grants
and hiding the practice from company auditors and shareholders.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Gullo in San Francisco at 
 kgullo@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        